{"tid":1896524,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★支：出招振樓市　杭州最高補貼800萬人幣","createTime":"2020-02-25T07:36:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T09:40:44.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"760095f5e636dc13652f505731bdf5497a33108d","tid":1896524,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:36:46.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎肆虐令中國置業需求延後，近期各省市推出的房地產調控政策由放鬆土地出讓政策，續漸轉向刺激買樓需求。據內地媒體報道，杭州市提高人才購房補貼，給予A類頂尖人才「一人一議」最高800萬元人民幣(下同)購房補貼；B、C、D類人才分別給予200萬元、150萬元、100萬元買樓補貼等。<br />\n<br />\n此外，對全球本科以上所有應屆大學生，在發放本科1萬元、碩士3萬元、博士5萬元一次過生活補助的基礎上，再給予每年1萬元租樓補貼，最多可享受6年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200225/bkn-20200225141743799-0225_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200225%2Fbkn-20200225141743799-0225_00842_001.html&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpQsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=029f405a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200225/bkn-20200225141743799-0225_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"db8e8601dca061a690a1742a3c500ba10187268c","tid":1896524,"uid":44171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:37:51.000Z","msg":"頭個月就中肺炎死鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2cc1e2fd96fdc81a93136c034f69861c2a17d9f","tid":1896524,"uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8HBfE7v.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8HBfE7v.gif&h=7fa8a128&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5989a4fa4df9bdd02d86c2932ba643fc2d0270c9","tid":1896524,"uid":13503,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:39:08.000Z","msg":"咁多鬼城免費住都得"},{"pid":"c36e3b63b233d753c91e6d1bb3dc975c945f485b","tid":1896524,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5989a4fa4df9bdd02d86