本科以上所有應屆大學生，在發放本科1萬元、碩士3萬元、博士5萬元一次過生活補助的基礎上，再給予每年1萬元租樓補貼，最多可享受6年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200225/bkn-20200225141743799-0225_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200225%2Fbkn-20200225141743799-0225_00842_001.html&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpQsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=029f405a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200225/bkn-20200225141743799-0225_00842_001.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:51:20.000Z","msg":"大家可能唔知<br />\n係買樓係要交稅<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">先收你房地產買賣稅</span><br />\n（人地印800萬比你，你要出錢交稅比返政府，人地出雞你出豉油）<br />\n<br />\n係大陸<span style=\"color: violet;\">擁有一層樓</span>，又係要交稅<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">類似香港既地租差餉，起碼年年5%以上</span>"},{"pid":"8a584b8016faa19e55142960ff437cf24e7433a2","tid":1896524,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:51:27.000Z","msg":"開始滯脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a8d1a34117cb523782088fc4a591679f248c438","tid":1896524,"uid":187544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9988b8fabf3c31f23ad28c4f400f68cbe9ca87ea","tid":1896524,"uid":82359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:50:20.000Z","msg":"即係可能本身賣50萬就mark高到900萬，再支助番你八百萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:52:17.000Z","msg":"世事都比你看透，然後其他人就乖乖打一世工供樓，唔好暴動呀"},{"pid":"372cfd06707e49bdbb4e0236bc13ccf19e4b2864","tid":1896524,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:52:53.000Z","msg":"點先做到A類人才"},{"pid":"b4da911ab7bcf0f6baead6ea010f5793311c837d","tid":1896524,"uid":312332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9988b8fabf3c31f23ad28c4f400f68cbe9ca87ea","tid":1896524,"uid":82359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:50:20.000Z","msg":"即係可能本身賣50萬就mark高到900萬，再支助番你八百萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T08:07:17.000Z","msg":"唔會咁玩囉<br />\n咪當大陸全部都低能<br />\n<br />\n你應該咁諗<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">房地產公司一早已經係國企</span><br />\n國企銀行同政府都大量入股呢類公司<br />\n<br />\n宜家房地產=國企=地方政府<br />\n出800萬比你買佢既屋，<br />\n你要交幾十萬稅比佢，年年要交5%以上既地租差餉比佢<br />\n佢間公司收佢自己印出黎既800萬，同時政府收百幾萬稅收<br />\n<br />\n政府: 收你百幾萬稅<br />\n公司: 收政府果800萬<br />\n你: 得到1間屋，支出百幾萬稅"},{"pid":"697c51481d41646fd6bb7495836fd2a0a0f24b49","tid":1896524,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T08:35:50.000Z","msg":"習主席:房子是用來住的。"},{"pid":"ff5a05bf7f3a8dbdd430f0df87f5059db3434482","tid":1896524,"uid":26424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"372cfd06707e49bdbb4e0236bc13ccf19e4b2864","tid":1896524,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:52:53.000Z","msg":"點先做到A類人才"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T08:50:39.000Z","msg":"Abel Prize<br />\nTuring Award<br />\nFields Medal<br />\nNobel Prize<br />\n其中一樣得奬<br />\n中國工程院 中國科學院院士"},{"pid":"fb2631a9df6ef4fc797ab7925daf8ba330b331e3","tid":1896524,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"697c51481d41646fd6bb7495836fd2a0a0f24b49","tid":1896524,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T08:35:50.000Z","msg":"習主席:房子是用來住的。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T08:52:04.000Z","msg":"淺水灣別墅呢？"},{"pid":"46ae3e66a810d9bc857af5d89c620427f08762f2","tid":1896524,"uid":152388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T08:54:00.000Z","msg":"遲d只準買唔準賣樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f601bef1cddf33abd96763f56e0475268cf80b59","tid":1896524,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff5a05bf7f3a8dbdd430f0df87f5059db3434482","tid":1896524,"uid":26424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"372cfd06707e49bdbb4e0236bc13ccf19e4b2864","tid":1896524,"uid":53062,"like":0,"